{"tid":1693872,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"周五「立冬」過後降溫　周六低見20℃","createTime":"2019-11-05T00:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T00:32:50.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"088a95330bb057fbc150e213e2934986cea4b672","tid":1693872,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191104/_2019110414143873108.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191104%2F_2019110414143873108.jpg&h=e33c0a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天文台表示，乾燥的東北季候風會在本周餘下時間為華南帶來普遍晴朗的天氣，早晚天氣稍涼。此外，一個廣闊低壓區會在未來兩三日於南海中南部徘徊並逐漸發展，該區天氣不穩定，風勢頗大。預料該低壓區會在本周後期移向越南中部。<br />\n<br />\n明日天晴乾燥，氣溫21至27度。周三大致天晴及乾燥，氣溫21至26度。周四天晴乾燥，氣溫22至27度。<br />\n<br />\n周五是廿四節氣中的「立冬」，天晴乾燥，氣溫21至27度。周六部分時間有陽光，日間乾燥，氣溫20至25度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1628679/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94-%E7%AB%8B%E5%86%AC-%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%AB-%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E4%BD%8E%E8%A6%8B20%E2%84%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1628679%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%2586%25AC-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%25BA%25AB-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%25A6%258B20%25E2%2584%2583&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=b38c2d20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1628679%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%2586%25AC-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%25BA%25AB-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%25A6%258B20%25E2%2584%2583&h=19679041\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1628679/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94-%E7%AB%8B%E5%86%AC-%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%AB-%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E4%BD%8E%E8%A6%8B20%E2%84%83</a>"}]}